OL,7,FTributes have been paid to former
OL,8,FAston Villa player Charlie Aitkin who
OL,9,Fhas died at the age of 81.
OL,11,FThe defender spent 17 years with the
OL,12,Fclub, during which time he made a
OL,13,Ftotal of 660 appearances ` 657 starts
OL,14,Fplus three as a substitute.
OL,16,FAitken also mirrored the club's
OL,17,Ffluctuating fortunes from the mid-
OL,18,F1960s to the mid-1970s, making the
OL,19,Fjourney from the old First Division
OL,20,Fto the Second to the Third ` and back
OL,21,Fagain ` between 1967 and 1975.
